    "description": "Takachiho Koheki Co.,Ltd. operates as a technology trading company in Japan. It offers mechanical component products, including slide rails, cable guides, conston springs, dampers, gas springs, lifting and cylinder lock systems, monitor arms, and other mechanical components; and semiconductor products, such as communication devices, power modules and devices, sensors, connectors, trans, coils, and GPU boards. The company also provides retail security products comprising electronic article surveillance, display product security, image surveillance, image analysis, store management, and remote monitoring systems, as well as source tagging labels; and business solution products consisting of WAN/LAN and network security products, as well as office security products, such as access control and properties removal management systems, and IP solutions/IP cameras/NVR systems. In addition, it offers video sensing cloud service, estimation for male and female customers, shelf browsing time service, and IQ Lane, a checkout service; and support, maintenance, operation and management, installation, and tuning solutions. The company was incorporated in 1952 and is headquartered in Shinjuku, Japan."
